Artuis is a versatile and flexible model, it allows you to generate crisp, high-resolution images:

To make unique faces, mix celebrity faces that the model knows: [emma stone : scarlett johansson : 0.5]

If you liked my model, please leave a review, it helps other users to find this model and see its features!

This is SD 2.1 based model, also I have SD 1.5 based version with more NSFW capabilities: https://civitai.com/models/47691/artiusv1-5

The model works best with the following samplers:
Euler a
DPM2
DPM++ 2M Karras

Optimal settings:
Clip skip 1
Eta noise seed delta: 31337
DPM++ 2M Karras
25 Steps
CFG Scale 6
Resolution from 768 (768, 1024, 1280)

The model is prompt sensitive, so it depends on your imagination.
I've generated some demo images, you can study the prompt and make your own based on them.
